  faqs={faqs}
  article={{
    headline: "Pyometra in Breeding Females: The Emergency Every Breeder Should Know About",
    description: "An educational guide to pyometra for dog, cat, goat, sheep, and horse breeders: the signs, open vs. closed forms, diagnosis, treatment, breeding implications, and the records that help in an emergency.",
