            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] mr-3 font-bold mt-1">•</span><span>Merck Veterinary Manual, <a href="https://www.merckvetmanual.com/reproductive-system/reproductive-diseases-of-the-female-small-animal/cystic-endometrial-hyperplasia-pyometra-complex-in-small-animals" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">Cystic Endometrial Hyperplasia-Pyometra Complex in Small Animals</a>.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] mr-3 font-bold mt-1">•</span><span>MSD/Merck Veterinary Manual, <a href="https://www.msdvetmanual.com/reproductive-system/uterine-diseases-in-production-animals/pyometra-in-production-animals" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">Pyometra in Production Animals</a>.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] mr-3 font-bold mt-1">•</span><span>Merck Veterinary Manual (Horse Owner version), <a href="https://www.merckvetmanual.com/horse-owners/reproductive-disorders-of-horses/pyometra-in-horses" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">Pyometra in Horses</a>.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] mr-3 font-bold mt-1">•</span><span>American College of Veterinary Surgeons (ACVS), <a href="https://www.acvs.org/small-animal/pyometra/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">Pyometra</a>.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] mr-3 font-bold mt-1">•</span><span>VCA Animal Hospitals, <a href="https://vcahospitals.com/know-your-pet/pyometra-in-dogs" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">Pyometra in Dogs</a> and <a href="https://vcahospitals.com/know-your-pet/pyometra-in-cats" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">Pyometra in Cats</a>.</span></li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed italic">
            Disclaimer: This article is provided for educational and informational purposes only and is not intended as veterinary medical advice. Animal health conditions can vary significantly by species, breed, age, and individual circumstances. If you suspect an animal may be experiencing pyometra or any other medical emergency, seek immediate evaluation from a licensed veterinarian. BreederHQ does not provide veterinary services, diagnoses, treatment recommendations, or medical advice.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </article>

